
Proxmox VE - T2 Mac Edition
============================
T2 hardware support included:
  Kernel  : pve-edge-kernel-t2 (apple-bce built in)
  WiFi    : broadcom-sta/wl driver (no Apple firmware needed â€” activated automatically)
  Audio   : apple-t2-audio-config
  Touch Bar: tiny-dfr (if installed)

WiFi is activated automatically at boot. Run /usr/bin/t2-wifi-firmware to check status.

After installation the T2 kernel will be set up automatically on first boot.

Sources: https://github.com/t2linux/wiki
         https://github.com/AdityaGarg8/pve-edge-kernel-t2

